beer.beer_description:
The West Coast of the US is synonymous with significant parts of pop culture. If you’ve been to SoCal, it's not surprising it laid the foundations for the West Coast hip hop scene and the West Coast IPA. There's nothing quite like slamming back a dank and hoppy West Coast IPA with a background soundtrack of West Coast hip hop legends like Pharcyde, Ice Cube, and Dr. Dre.

This beer is our tribute to the SoCal scene, dreams, and vibes. SoCal Thirst is our modern take on a classic style. Hopped with Amarillo, Centennial, and Citra that results in an aromatic blend of pine, citrus, and floral notes. It boasts prominent grapefruit and stone-fruit flavours that are deliciously balanced by a satisfyingly firm bitter finish.

Try 5 more for Level 14!

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 30 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 7!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 45 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 10!

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 160 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 33! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
